#: ../../source/pytest.rst:2
msgid "Pytest plugin"
msgstr "Плагин для Pytest"

#: ../../source/pytest.rst:6
msgid ""
"All pytest plugin code lives in the ``aiomisc`` package itself. The "
"aiomisc-pytest_ package is required only for plugin registration (it "
"contains the pytest entry point). Install both:"
msgstr ""
"Весь код плагина pytest находится в пакете ``aiomisc``. "
"Пакет aiomisc-pytest_ нужен только для регистрации плагина "
"(содержит точку входа pytest). Установите оба пакета:"

#: ../../source/pytest.rst:10
msgid "pip install aiomisc aiomisc-pytest"
msgstr "pip install aiomisc aiomisc-pytest"

#: ../../source/pytest.rst:15
msgid "Basic usage"
msgstr "Базовое использование"

#: ../../source/pytest.rst:17
msgid ""
"The plugin automatically provides an event loop and an entrypoint for "
"every async test. Simply write ``async def test_...`` functions:"
msgstr ""
"Плагин автоматически предоставляет цикл событий и entrypoint для каждого "
"асинхронного теста. Просто пишите функции ``async def test_...``:"

#: ../../source/pytest.rst:20
msgid ""
"async def test_sample(event_loop):\n"
"    f = event_loop.create_future()\n"
"    event_loop.call_soon(f.set_result, True)\n"
"    assert await f"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/pytest.rst:27
msgid "Async fixtures work the same way:"
msgstr "Асинхронные фикстуры работают аналогично:"

#: ../../source/pytest.rst:29
msgid ""
"import asyncio\n"
"import pytest\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"@pytest.fixture\n"
"async def my_fixture():\n"
"    await asyncio.sleep(0)\n"
"    yield \"value\"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"async def test_with_fixture(my_fixture):\n"
"    assert my_fixture == \"value\""
msgstr ""

